4 HR____ COMMENDING ANNA GRACE TUCKER ON HER COMMUNITY SERVICE
5 INITIATIVE BRINGING AWARENESS TO AND SUPPORTING YOUTH WITH
6 SPEECH DISORDERS.
7
8 WHEREAS, with great pride and deep appreciation, we
9 recognize individuals who bring awareness to community
10 service initiatives that support and encourage young people,
11 because the strength of our future depends on how we pour
12 into our children and our youth; and
13 WHEREAS, Miss Anna Grace Tucker is a junior business
14 major at Troy University, where she proudly serves as Miss
15 Troy University 2026; before earning her current title, she
16 was honored to represent her alma mater as Miss Southern
17 Union 2025, demonstrating her commitment to leadership,
18 service, and personal excellence; and
19 WHEREAS, at Troy, Anna Grace is an active member of
20 the M.I.S.S. Elite Organization, a group dedicated to
21 empowering women through mentorship and service; she also
22 shines as a member of the Troy University Dance Line, where
23 her talent and school spirit radiate both on and off the
24 field; and
25 WHEREAS, her community service initiative, "Say It
26 Out Loud," focuses on bringing awareness to and supporting
27 youth with speech disorders; through this platform, Anna
28 Grace advocates for confidence, communication, and inclusion
Page 1

Grace advocates for confidence, communication, and inclusion
