29 by encouraging young people everywhere to embrace their
30 voices and speak boldly; and
31 WHEREAS, with a heart for service and a passion for
32 purpose, Anna Grace continues to inspire others through her
33 dedication, authenticity, and unwavering belief in the power
34 of self-expression; now therefore,
35 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
36 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That Miss Anna Grace Tucker is
37 hereby commended for her community service initiative
38 supporting and advocating for youth with speech disorders,
39 so that they may reach their full potential with confidence
40 and assurance.
